elementValueMap.BHealthCountFailed: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle')) && EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseBHealthChange%,'Yes - See Behavioral Health Related List For Changes') &&  EQUALS(%BHealthCount%,0),'Failed','NA')
elementValueMap.BHealthCountPassed: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle')) && EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseBHealthChange%,'Yes - See Behavioral Health Related List For Changes') &&  %BHealthCount%>0,'Passed','NA')
elementValueMap.BHealthFailedText: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle')) && EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseBHealthChange%,'Yes - See Behavioral Health Related List For Changes') && %BHealthCount%=0,"Rule: Since the field “Are There Changes To Behavioral Health” = Yes, you must have at least one Behavioral Health record on the Related List off the Implementation Case : ",'NA')
elementValueMap.BHealthSuccessText: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle')) && EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseBHealthChange%,'Yes - See Behavioral Health Related List For Changes') && %BHealthCount%>0,"Rule: Since the field “Are There Changes To Behavioral Health” = Yes, you must have at least one Behavioral Health record on the Related List off the Implementation Case : ",'NA')
elementValueMap.BillingFailedText: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle')) && EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseBillingChange%,'Yes') && %ImplementationCaseFundingCount%=0,"Rule: Since the field “Changes To Funding Or Billing Entity” = Yes, you must have at least one Billing Entity record for the Group :   ",'NA')
elementValueMap.BillingSucessText: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle')) && EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseBillingChange%,'Yes') && %ImplementationCaseFundingCount%>0,"Rule: Since the field “Changes To Funding Or Billing Entity” = Yes, you must have at least one Billing Entity record for the Group : ",'NA')
elementValueMap.FundingFailedText: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle')) && EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseBillingChange%,'Yes') && %ImplementationCaseFunding%='NA',"Rule: Since the field “Changes To Funding Or Billing Entity” = Yes, you must complete the “Indicate Funding Record (WGS)” field :  ",'NA')
elementValueMap.FundingSuccessText: =IF(OR(EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Renewal'),EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseType%,'Change Request Off Cycle'))  && EQUALS(%ImplementationCaseBillingChange%,'Yes') && %ImplementationCaseFundingCount%!='NA',"Rule: Since the field “Changes To Funding Or Billing Entity” = Yes, you must complete the “Indicate Funding Record (WGS)” field :  ",'NA')
